metadata.name: Deep Prism
metadata.description:
-Deep Prism reflects the color spectrum in a magnificent way. This multimedia fine art piece has been minted as the first piece in the Dope Colors NFT collection for obvious reasons. 

-The all inclusive colors and sparkling background shed light into the greatness of beauty contained in this work. The objective of the piece is to better display colors in motion, and how they can have a positive impact when being viewed.
